OL,4,CChildren speak of sickness and neglect
OL,5,Cin US asylum camps
OL,6, The US has a vast system of detention
OL,7, sites scattered across the country,
OL,8, holding more than 20,000 migrant
OL,9, children. In a special investigation,
OL,10, the BBC has uncovered allegations of
OL,11, cold temperatures, sickness, neglect,
OL,12, lice and filth, through a series of
OL,13, interviews with children and staff.
OL,15,FIt was midnight on the Rio Grande - the
OL,16,Fimposing river that forms the border
OL,17,Fbetween Texas and Mexico - and lights
OL,18,Fbegan to flash on the Mexican side.
OL,19,FVoices could be heard in the darkness.
OL,20,FFigures emerged, got into a small raft,
OL,21,Fand began to cross the river.
